</style><script>
  // Queue messages until React hydration completes to prevent hydration mismatches
  let isHydrated = false;
  const messageQueue = [];

  function beehiiv_messageHandler(event) {
    if (event.data && event.data.type === 'beehiiv:iframe_height') {
      if (!isHydrated) {
        // Queue message until hydration completes
        messageQueue.push(event);
        return;
      }

      let iframe = null;

      // Try embedId first (works for sandboxed iframes in editor)
      if (event.data.embedId) {
        iframe = document.getElementById(event.data.embedId);
        if (iframe) {
          // The embed div contains the iframe, so find it
          iframe = iframe.querySelector('iframe');
        }
      }

      // Fallback to frameElement (works for non-sandboxed iframes on published sites)
      if (!iframe && event.source) {
        try {
          iframe = event.source.frameElement;
        } catch (e) {
          // frameElement access fails for sandboxed iframes (cross-origin)
        }
      }

      if (iframe && event.data.height) {
        iframe.style.height = event.data.height + 'px';
      }
    }
  }

  window.addEventListener('message', beehiiv_messageHandler);

  // Wait for React hydration to complete before processing queued messages
  // Listen for custom event dispatched after hydration completes
  document.addEventListener('beehiiv:hydration_completed', () => {
    isHydrated = true;
    messageQueue.forEach(event => beehiiv_messageHandler(event));
    messageQueue.length = 0;
  });

class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5"/></picture></div></div><div id="employee-retention-starts-with-cult" class="hynlcx0"><h3 class="hynlcx1 hynlcx4" translations="[object Object]"><span class="hxnnnr0">Employee retention starts with culture, not compensation alone.</span></h3></div><div class="j6zgbu0"><p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"><span class="hxnnnr0">At Paradise Chevrolet Cadillac, half the workforce has stayed for over a decade because leadership invests in people-first initiatives that go beyond paychecks.</span></p></div><div class="_1gqvddm0" style="border-color:#222222;border-style:solid;border-radius:2px;border-width:0px;--post-section-background-color:#F8F5E9;--post-section-margin-top:16px;--post-section-margin-left:0px;--post-section-margin-right:0px;--post-section-margin-bottom:16px;--post-section-padding-top:24px;--post-section-padding-left:24px;--post-section-padding-right:24px;--post-section-padding-bottom:24px"><div class="dream-post-content-blockquoteFigure yuqx92" translations="[object Object]"><div class="dream-post-content-blockquoteFigure yuqx95" translations="[object Object]"><div class="dream-post-content-quote _1xtprv90" translations="[object Object]"><div class="_1xtprv91">❝</div><div class="j6zgbu0"><p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"><span class="hxnnnr0">&quot;We can have the best process in place for great customer service but if you have unhappy employees, you&#x27;re going to have no one to execute it.&quot;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="j6zgbu0"><p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"><span class="hxnnnr0">That’s why the dealership gives Rolexes to 30-year employees, awards a car at their annual Christmas party, and offers free gym memberships plus mental health resources.</span></p></div><div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0" style="--caption-alignment:center"><div class="_2fealp1"><picture><source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5"/></picture></div></div><div class="hynlcx0"><h3 class="hynlcx1 hynlcx4" translations="[object Object]"><span class="hxnnnr0">Working in roles beats shadowing them when preparing for leadership.</span></h3></div><div class="j6zgbu0"><p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"><span class="hxnnnr0">Succession planning works best when future leaders experience every department firsthand rather than just observing from the sidelines.</span></p></div><div class="_1gqvddm0" style="border-color:#222222;border-style:solid;border-radius:2px;border-width:0px;--post-section-background-color:#F8F5E9;--post-section-margin-top:16px;--post-section-margin-left:0px;--post-section-margin-right:0px;--post-section-margin-bottom:16px;--post-section-padding-top:24px;--post-section-padding-left:24px;--post-section-padding-right:24px;--post-section-padding-bottom:24px"><div srcSet="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/e509276b-f92a-4877-885a-df5b6c640d8a/divider-09.png 2x"/><source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcSet="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/e509276b-f92a-4877-885a-df5b6c640d8a/divider-09.png 1x"/><img src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/e509276b-f92a-4877-885a-df5b6c640d8a/divider-09.png" alt="" style="width:100%" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5"/></picture></div></div><div class="hynlcx0"><h3 class="hynlcx1 hynlcx4" translations="[object Object]"><span class="hxnnnr0">Inconsistent onboarding costs money through preventable turnover.</span></h3></div><div class="j6zgbu0"><p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"><span class="hxnnnr0">When new hires receive different information depending on who trains them, it creates confusion that leads to early departures and wasted investment.</span></p></div><div class="_1gqvddm0" style="border-color:#222222;border-style:solid;border-radius:2px;border-width:0px;--post-section-background-color:#F8F5E9;--post-section-margin-top:16px;--post-section-margin-left:0px;--post-section-margin-right:0px;--post-section-margin-bottom:16px;--post-section-padding-top:24px;--post-section-padding-left:24px;--post-section-padding-right:24px;--post-section-padding-bottom:24px"><div class="dream-post-content-blockquoteFigure yuqx92" translations="[object Object]"><div class="dream-post-content-blockquoteFigure yuqx95" translations="[object Object]"><div class="dream-post-content-quote _1xtprv90" translations="[object Object]"><div class="_1xtprv91">❝</div><div class="j6zgbu0"><p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"><span class="hxnnnr0">&quot;I could walk in the door and talk to one person, but then if someone else walks in the door, they could talk to five other people with different questions each time.&quot;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="j6zgbu0"><p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"><span class="hxnnnr0">Standardizing the onboarding process with recurring NCM or NADA training ensures every employee gets the same foundation, reducing costly turnover from avoidable mistakes.</span></p></div><div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0" style="--caption-alignment:center"><div class="_2fealp1"><picture><source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcSet="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/2242462f-eeb6-4cfa-b46e-825825d4eac8/divider-10.png 2x"/><source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcSet="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/2242462f-eeb6-4cfa-b46e-825825d4eac8/divider-10.png 1x"/><source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcSet="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/2242462f-eeb6-4cfa-b46e-825825d4eac8/divider-10.png 2x"/><source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcSet="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/2242462f-eeb6-4cfa-b46e-825825d4eac8/divider-10.png 1x"/><img src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/2242462f-eeb6-4cfa-b46e-825825d4eac8/divider-10.png" alt="" style="width:100%" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5"/></picture></div></div><div class="hynlcx0"><h3 class="hynlcx1 hynlcx4" translations="[object Object]"><span class="hxnnnr0">Local 20 groups provide unexpected business development opportunities.</span></h3></div><div class="j6zgbu0"><p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"><span class="hxnnnr0">Joining a non-automotive local CEO group with chamber presidents and hospital board members creates cross-promotional benefits that traditional 20 groups cannot offer.</span></p></div><div class="_1gqvddm0" style="border-color:#222222;border-style:solid;border-radius:2px;border-width:0px;--post-section-background-color:#F8F5E9;--post-section-margin-top:16px;--post-section-margin-left:0px;--post-section-margin-right:0px;--post-section-margin-bottom:16px;--post-section-padding-top:24px;--post-section-padding-left:24px;--post-section-padding-right:24px;--post-section-padding-bottom:24px"><div class="dream-post-content-blockquoteFigure yuqx92" translations="[object Object]"><div class="dream-post-content-blockquoteFigure yuqx95" translations="[object Object]"><div class="dream-post-content-quote _1xtprv90" translations="[object Object]"><div class="_1xtprv91">❝</div><div class="j6zgbu0"><p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"><span class="hxnnnr0">&quot;The value in that is something similar to being a part of the chamber in your local town, or in the Rotary because. You get to connect with other business owners who can then funnel your own business.&quot;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="j6zgbu0"><p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"><span class="hxnnnr0">While manufacturer 20 groups help with best practices and compliance, local business groups turn fellow members into potential customers and strong referral sources.</span></p></div><div style="--list-style-type:none"><div><div class="_1gbf4vw7"><h3 class="_1gbf4vw5">Did you enjoy this Podcast Recap newsletter?</h3><div class="_1gbf4vw6">Tell us why or
